<div id="review_3068328557" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3068328557" />
    <a title="Barbara K" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/93114967-barbara-k"><img alt="Barbara K" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1551265103p2/93114967.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3068328557?book_show_action=true">Dec 03, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Barbara K" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Barbara K" href="/user/show/93114967-barbara-k">Barbara K</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="MP3 Book 9781572706132" href="/book/show/10255505-what-i-believe">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/93114967-barbara-k?shelf=spiritual-religious">spiritual-religious</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3068328557" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11433550038800457641">Stimulating reading. On one level it is difficult to think that in 1940 Russell was deemed unfit to teach based on these brilliantly expressed ideas. And yet... Given the current socio-political climate in the US, I guess it shouldn’t be that hard to believe that people will overreact to concepts they find threatening. Something Russell himself understood completely. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review3068328557">
  <td colspan="2">
